 <span data-ttu-id="19662-105">**Navigationslebensdauer**: <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.Navigating>, <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.Navigated>, und <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.LoadCompleted>.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="19662-105">**Navigation Lifetime**: <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.Navigating>, <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.Navigated>, and <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.LoadCompleted>.</span></span>  
  
